<a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1120&endYear=1127')\">1120-1127年</a>，随父住秀州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1128&endYear=1128')\">1128年</a>，日诵书三千言。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"a7588aeaef3f427987effb424eb78d60\");'><span id='a7588aeaef3f427987effb424eb78d60_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1137')\">1129-1137年</a>，12-20岁</div><div id='a7588aeaef3f427987effb424eb78d60' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年</a>，以父出使恩补修职郎。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1131')\">1130-1131年</a>，或在秀州家居。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1132&endYear=1132')\">1132年</a>，诏下秀州，存问家属。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1133&endYear=1134')\">1133-1134年</a>，当在秀州家居。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1135&endYear=1135')\">1135年</a>，以修职郎监南岳庙。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1136&endYear=1136')\">1136年</a>，当在秀州家居。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1137&endYear=1137')\">1137年7月</a>，作戒蛇文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>戒蛇文。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-353页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1137&endYear=1137')\">1137年</a>，长子槻生。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"065c804aee104f5d93bd6a97a28febde\");'><span id='065c804aee104f5d93bd6a97a28febde_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1138&endYear=1138')\">1138年</a>，21岁</div><div id='065c804aee104f5d93bd6a97a28febde' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1138&endYear=1138')\">1138年</a>，母卒于秀州，还家秀州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":29.011281,"Longitude":116.709997,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN361128","Title":"鄱阳","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"bcbd3e241bb64a5eb71fcec9dd256765\");'><span id='bcbd3e241bb64a5eb71fcec9dd256765_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年</a>，12岁</div><div id='bcbd3e241bb64a5eb71fcec9dd256765' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年</a>，能任家事，率五弟三妹奉祖母及母避兵饶州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":29.481104,"Longitude":119.287608,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN330182","Title":"建德","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"b750ea4cfa034713b1bd1d1097c2a7fb\");'><span id='b750ea4cfa034713b1bd1d1097c2a7fb_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1137&endYear=1138')\">1137-1138年</a>，20-21岁</div><div id='b750ea4cfa034713b1bd1d1097c2a7fb' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1137&endYear=1137')\">1137年</a>，调严州录事参军。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1138&endYear=1138')\">1138年11月23日</a>，在严州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.496704,"Longitude":120.318954,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3202","Title":"无锡","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"8eac59985f544e339909a52b8808f06d\");'><span id='8eac59985f544e339909a52b8808f06d_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1139&endYear=1140')\">1139-1140年</a>，22-23岁</div><div id='8eac59985f544e339909a52b8808f06d' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1139&endYear=1139')\">1139年11月</a>，葬母于无锡县开化乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1140&endYear=1140')\">1140年</a>，丁忧。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.304566,"Longitude":120.589613,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3205","Title":"苏州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"b5ceda24ecba4996861eddbc26d5fadd\");'><span id='b5ceda24ecba4996861eddbc26d5fadd_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1141&endYear=1141')\">1141年</a>，24岁</div><div id='b5ceda24ecba4996861eddbc26d5fadd' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1141&endYear=1141')\">1141年</a>，除浙西提举常平司干办公事。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1141&endYear=1141')\">1141年</a>，时河南复为王土，拟宰臣贺表，仲舅沈松年一见而奇之，勉以习宏词科。<span class='label'>作品：</span>宰臣贺表。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-361页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1141&endYear=1141')\">1141年</a>，作《蛰寮记》。<span class='label'>作品：</span>蛰寮记。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-362页。）</span><br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"2d43f278815c48489b77d64f0b4b49bd\");'><span id='2d43f278815c48489b77d64f0b4b49bd_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1161&endYear=1162')\">1161-1162年</a>，44-45岁</div><div id='2d43f278815c48489b77d64f0b4b49bd' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1161&endYear=1161')\">1161年3月</a>，到平江。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1162&endYear=1162')\">1162年3月</a>，车驾亲征至建康，适上殿奏事。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1162&endYear=1162')\">1162年4月19日</a>，除尚书户部郎中，总领淮东军马钱粮。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.280059,"Longitude":120.161693,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3301","Title":"杭州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"b9004ea5003542da84eee52eb17e1705\");'><span id='b9004ea5003542da84eee52eb17e1705_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1142&endYear=1143')\">1142-1143年</a>，25-26岁</div><div id='b9004ea5003542da84eee52eb17e1705' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1142&endYear=1142')\">1142年</a>，与弟遵同试博学宏词科，名在第三。试题有《代枢密使谢赐玉带表》、《克敌弓铭》、《皇叔庆远军承宣使授昭化军节度使封安定郡王同知大宗正事制》、《唐勤政务本楼记》、《周成王搜岐阳颂》、《汉五家要说章句》。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《代枢密使谢赐玉带表》、《克敌弓铭》、《皇叔庆远军承宣使授昭化军节度使封安定郡王同知大宗正事制》、《唐勤政务本楼记》、《周成王搜岐阳颂》、《汉五家要说章句》。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-363页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1142&endYear=1142')\">1142年</a>，除左宣教郎敕令所删定官。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1143&endYear=1143')\">1143年</a>，以敕令所书成，拜秘书省正字。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"08424238d060430c97fedc96a1d7903e\");'><span id='08424238d060430c97fedc96a1d7903e_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1164&endYear=1164')\">1164年</a>，47岁</div><div id='08424238d060430c97fedc96a1d7903e' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1164&endYear=1164')\">1164年2月</a>，自淮东召还，除太常少卿。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1164&endYear=1164')\">1164年4月</a>，以太常少卿兼权直学士院。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1164&endYear=1164')\">1164年</a>，兼权礼部侍郎。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1164&endYear=1164')\">1164年11月</a>，兼直学士院。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"660d16a01b0c4d92939dc9f24939c431\");'><span id='660d16a01b0c4d92939dc9f24939c431_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1165&endYear=1166')\">1165-1166年</a>，48-49岁</div><div id='660d16a01b0c4d92939dc9f24939c431' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1165&endYear=1165')\">1165年5月</a>，礼成而还。除翰林学士、左中大夫、知制诰，仍兼中书舍人。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1165&endYear=1165')\">1165年</a>，除端明殿学士签枢密院事。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1165&endYear=1165')\">1165年8月</a>，除左中大夫参知政事兼权知枢密院事。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1165&endYear=1165')\">1165年10月</a>，充册立皇太子礼仪使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1165&endYear=1165')\">1165年12月</a>，拜左通奉大夫尚书右仆射同中书门下平章事兼枢密使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1166&endYear=1166')\">1166年3月</a>，以久雨引咎，三上章乞退。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1166&endYear=1166')\">1166年3月</a>，辛未，除观文殿学士提举江州太平兴国宫。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":29.294384,"Longitude":121.436043,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN330226","Title":"宁海","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e1313e89301d44628d534fcf2d6cc1a4\");'><span id='e1313e89301d44628d534fcf2d6cc1a4_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1144&endYear=1147')\">1144-1147年</a>，27-30岁</div><div id='e1313e89301d44628d534fcf2d6cc1a4' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1144&endYear=1144')\">1144年</a>，行县至宁海，题三瑞堂。<span class='label'>作品：</span>题三瑞堂诗。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-368页。）</span><div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">三瑞堂（宋·洪适）<br />　　五言律诗　押阳韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->久矣驰魂梦，今登三瑞堂。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->故山有乔木，近事话甘棠。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->展骥惭充位，占熊忆问祥。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->白云留未去，极望是吾乡。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1145&endYear=1145')\">1145年</a>，在台州任。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1146&endYear=1146')\">1146年</a>，在台州任。为张伯寿作《万养堂记》。<span class='label'>作品：</span>万养堂记。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-370页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1147&endYear=1147')\">1147年</a>，通判台州将满，与郡守不相能，十一月被殿中侍御史余尧弼论罢。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":24.191959,"Longitude":113.421493,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN441881","Title":"英德","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"7a00453775ae4e919e9f026f907a88fb\");'><span id='7a00453775ae4e919e9f026f907a88fb_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1148&endYear=1149')\">1148-1149年</a>，31-32岁</div><div id='7a00453775ae4e919e9f026f907a88fb' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1148&endYear=1148')\">1148年</a>，往来岭南侍侯父亲，凡九年。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1149&endYear=1149')\">1149年</a>，在英州侍父。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"9eb695aeceba40f9a3ff72836777d412\");'><span id='9eb695aeceba40f9a3ff72836777d412_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1151&endYear=1154')\">1151-1154年</a>，34-37岁</div><div id='9eb695aeceba40f9a3ff72836777d412' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1151&endYear=1151')\">1151年2月22日</a>，作《通天岩记》。<span class='label'>作品：</span>通天岩记。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-377页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1152&endYear=1154')\">1152-1154年</a>，在英州侍父。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":25.837179,"Longitude":114.94126,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3607","Title":"赣州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"885a39ee9bbf42c282f4a4fdc8ccc7e0\");'><span id='885a39ee9bbf42c282f4a4fdc8ccc7e0_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1150&endYear=1150')\">1150年</a>，33岁</div><div id='885a39ee9bbf42c282f4a4fdc8ccc7e0' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1150&endYear=1150')\">1150年12月1日</a>，舟泊虔州，有纪梦一篇。<span class='label'>作品：</span>纪梦。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-374页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1150&endYear=1150')\">1150年</a>，作《嘉济庙碑》<span class='label'>作品：</span>嘉济庙碑。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-375页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1150&endYear=1150')\">1150年</a>，作《知政桥记》。<span class='label'>作品：</span>知政桥记。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-376页。）</span><br /></div>"},{"Latitude":25.125335,"Longitude":114.317421,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN440282","Title":"南雄","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"a1aeaf623f424a0d93088920d0e4a6ff\");'><span id='a1aeaf623f424a0d93088920d0e4a6ff_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1155&endYear=1155')\">1155年</a>，38岁</div><div id='a1aeaf623f424a0d93088920d0e4a6ff' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1155&endYear=1155')\">1155年</a>，父皓卒于南雄途次。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":28.968047,"Longitude":117.135438,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN360281","Title":"乐平","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"bf328f2477e34aa6b5d0dfb6dcaaa9bb\");'><span id='bf328f2477e34aa6b5d0dfb6dcaaa9bb_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1156&endYear=1157')\">1156-1157年</a>，39-40岁</div><div id='bf328f2477e34aa6b5d0dfb6dcaaa9bb' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1156&endYear=1156')\">1156年11月</a>，葬父于故乡。<span class='label'>作品：</span>先君述。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-382页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1157&endYear=1157')\">1157年</a>，丁忧居家。为其父制十六尊者像作偈。<span class='label'>作品：</span>报庵十六尊者偈。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-383页。）</span><br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"796d8d63e8344fc1bd9442bc15b85529\");'><span id='796d8d63e8344fc1bd9442bc15b85529_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1169&endYear=1184')\">1169-1184年</a>，52-67岁</div><div id='796d8d63e8344fc1bd9442bc15b85529' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1169&endYear=1170')\">1169-1170年</a>，家居。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1171&endYear=1171')\">1171年</a>，诗有“于越归来三见春”之句。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1172&endYear=1172')\">1172年5月</a>，作《盘洲记》，自称盘洲老人。<span class='label'>作品：</span>盘洲记。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-425页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1172&endYear=1172')\">1172年</a>，时连年水旱，流移系道，适抚恤贫困，宗族称之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1173&endYear=1173')\">1173年</a>，作《楚望楼上梁文》<span class='label'>作品：</span>楚望楼上梁文。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-427页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1174&endYear=1175')\">1174-1175年</a>，家居。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1176&endYear=1176')\">1176年</a>，作《容膝斋上梁文》。<span class='label'>作品：</span>容膝斋上梁文。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-430页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1176&endYear=1176')\">1176年</a>，增改《隶释》千余字。令次子刊正之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1176&endYear=1176')\">1176年12月25日</a>，落一左齿，有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>丙申腊二十五日落一左齿。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-432页。）</span><div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">丙申腊二十五日落一左齿（宋·洪适）<br />　　七言绝句　</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->行年六十已中枯，雪映衰髯岁且除。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->一齿骤然离左辅，益怜大嚼远庖厨。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1177&endYear=1177')\">1177年6月</a>，跋《岐阳石鼓文》<span class='label'>作品：</span>《岐阳石鼓文》跋。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-433页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1177&endYear=1177')\">1177年7月24日</a>，夜梦至一萧寺，有记。<span class='label'>作品：</span>记梦。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-434页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1178&endYear=1178')\">1178年</a>，家居。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1179&endYear=1179')\">1179年8月21日</a>，妻莱国夫人沈氏薨。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1179&endYear=1179')\">1179年</a>，李秀叔知绍兴府，增刻《隶续》五卷，通判喻良能为跋。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1180&endYear=1180')\">1180年8月</a>，有劾管璆劄子。<span class='label'>作品：</span>劾管璆劄子。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-438页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1180&endYear=1180')\">1180年</a>，尤袤刻《隶续》二卷于江东仓台。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1181&endYear=1181')\">1181年6月</a>，编次《淳熙隶释》五十卷成，自题其后。<span class='label'>作品：</span>淳熙隶释跋。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-440页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1181&endYear=1181')\">1181年10月</a>，葬莱国夫人。自作小传。<span class='label'>作品：</span>莱国墓铭。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-441页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1182&endYear=1183')\">1182-1183年</a>，家居。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1184&endYear=1184')\">1184年2月</a>，二月辛酉，薨。自罢相后累加恩爵至鄱阳郡开国公食邑五千二百户实封二千四百户赠特进累赠太师魏国公。谥文惠。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.041792,"Longitude":112.205843,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4208","Title":"荆门","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"34e667532a314e518d0b3eafad68b7ff\");'><span id='34e667532a314e518d0b3eafad68b7ff_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1159')\">1158-1159年</a>，41-42岁</div><div id='34e667532a314e518d0b3eafad68b7ff' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年4月</a>，服阕，四月除知荆门军。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年6月</a>，到任。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年9月</a>，应诏上宽恤四事。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，在荆门任。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":29.866822,"Longitude":118.420057,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN341021","Title":"歙县","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"cbc484cf20c245ff8ff029cad15e44a4\");'><span id='cbc484cf20c245ff8ff029cad15e44a4_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1161')\">1159-1161年</a>，42-44岁</div><div id='cbc484cf20c245ff8ff029cad15e44a4' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，其秋，以左朝奉郎借紫知徽州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年9月16日</a>，到徽州任。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1160&endYear=1160')\">1160年</a>，在徽州任。转左朝请郎。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1160&endYear=1160')\">1160年</a>，范成大为州司户参军，适一见而知其远器，勉以吏事，与商榷古今，谓成大他日必登两府。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1160&endYear=1160')\">1160年</a>，刻《砚说》三种。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1161&endYear=1161')\">1161年2月29日</a>，除提举浙西常平茶盐。甫到任，改除提举江东路常平茶盐兼提点刑狱。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.195688,"Longitude":119.431494,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3211","Title":"镇江","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"be4cadd8226f4af4b1d6275494ba306c\");'><span id='be4cadd8226f4af4b1d6275494ba306c_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1162&endYear=1163')\">1162-1163年</a>，45-46岁</div><div id='be4cadd8226f4af4b1d6275494ba306c' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1162&endYear=1162')\">1162年4月26日</a>，到京口任。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1163&endYear=1163')\">1163年</a>，在淮东总领任。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1163&endYear=1163')\">1163年</a>，迁司农少卿。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1163&endYear=1163')\">1163年</a>，筑得江楼、花信亭于镇江公廨。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":39.911013,"Longitude":116.413554,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN11","Title":"北京","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"eb966b6d604143269aec9495841ad81f\");'><span id='eb966b6d604143269aec9495841ad81f_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1164&endYear=1165')\">1164-1165年</a>，47-48岁</div><div id='eb966b6d604143269aec9495841ad81f' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1164&endYear=1164')\">1164年12月</a>，金人讲和，假礼部尚书，充贺金生辰使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1165&endYear=1165')\">1165年3月</a>，到燕京馆。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.036519,"Longitude":120.586673,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3306","Title":"绍兴","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"8b964e6ef0dd446198fadf7b070e9983\");'><span id='8b964e6ef0dd446198fadf7b070e9983_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1166&endYear=1168')\">1166-1168年</a>，49-51岁</div><div id='8b964e6ef0dd446198fadf7b070e9983' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1166&endYear=1166')\">1166年7月18日</a>，以观文殿学士左通奉大夫知绍兴府浙东安抚使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1167&endYear=1167')\">1167年</a>，在绍兴任。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1167&endYear=1167')\">1167年1月8日</a>，序《隶释》刻之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>隶释序。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-416页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1167&endYear=1167')\">1167年</a>，刻《论衡》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1168&endYear=1168')\">1168年</a>，在绍兴任。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1168&endYear=1168')\">1168年</a>，刻《元氏长庆集》六十卷于郡斋，为文序之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>元氏长庆集序。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册,第307-419页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1168&endYear=1168')\">1168年</a>，刻《隶续》十卷。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1168&endYear=1168')\">1168年3月</a>，再上章请祠。三月以观文殿学士提举临安府洞霄宫。自是家居者十六年。<br /></div>"}],"Title":"洪适 <span class='inlineComment2'>(1117-1184)</span>","Detail":"<p class='inlineComment2'>引用书目：钱大昕《洪文惠公年谱》　录入整理：凌郁之</p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(0, 4, 119.0684965, 29.7066045, 8)\">0-20岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(0)\">台州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(1)\">嘉兴</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2)\">鄱阳</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(3)\">嘉兴</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(4, 12, 117.428768, 27.8443315, 8)\">20-32岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(4)\">建德</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(5)\">嘉兴</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(6)\">无锡</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(7)\">苏州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(8)\">杭州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(9)\">台州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(10)\">宁海</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(11)\">英德</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(12, 21, 116.397728, 28.1938235, 7)\">33-47岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(12)\">赣州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(13)\">英德</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(14)\">南雄</a> → <a href=\"j